data.description: This beautiful home is located in a family-friendly community of McKinney and zoned in the highly-rated Prosper-ISD! Notable home features include an open floor plan, kitchen with granite countertop, a large island, and a spacious back yard with built-in covered patio! Awesome Community Pool and Playground located within minutes. All appliances, 80” TV in primary living room, and TV on back patio convey with this home.
